Portug side Porto beat Bayern Munich 3-1 in the Champions League quarter-final first leg . 
  Julen Lopetegui has masterminded an unbeaten Champions League campaign . 
  Ricardo Quaresma scored twice in the first leg at the Dragao Stadium . 
  Jose Mourinho led Porto to Champions League glory in 2004 . 
  The Portuguese side are unbeaten in the competition this season . 
 